{{Infobox book | name = Agatha Christie's Secret Notebooks | image = Agatha Christie's Secret Notebooks.jpg | author = John Curran | genre = [[Non-fiction novel|Non-fiction]], [[Crime (genre)|Crime]] | published = 2009 | publisher = [[HarperCollins]] | isbn = 978-0-007-31056-2 | alt = Agatha Christie's Secret Notebooks | pages = 492 | awards = [[Anthony Award|Anthony Award for Best Critical Nonfiction]] (2011) }}
'''Agatha Christie's Secret Notebooks''': ''Fifty Years of Mysteries in the Making'' is a book written by John Curran<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=ajPiyweL678C|title=Agatha Christie's Secret Notebooks: Fifty Years of Mysteries in the Making - Includes Two Unpublished Poirot Stories|last=Curran|first=John|date=2009-09-06|publisher=HarperCollins Publishers|isbn=9780007310586|language=en}}</ref> and published by [[HarperCollins]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.harpercollins.com/9780061988370/agatha-christies-secret-notebooks|title=Agatha Christie's Secret Notebooks - John Curran - Paperback|last=Curran|first=John|website=HarperCollins US|language=en|access-date=2017-03-27}}</ref> on 6 September 2009, which later went on to win the [[Anthony Award]] for Best Critical Nonfiction in 2011.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bouchercon.com/anthony-awards/winners-and-nominees/|title=Winners and Nominees|date=2015-08-10|work=Bouchercon|access-date=2017-03-27|language=en}}</ref>
A sequel, titled Murder in the Making, was published by HarperCollins in 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.harpercollins.com/9780062065438/agatha-christie-murder-in-the-making|title=Agatha Christie: Murder in the Making - John Curran - Paperback|publisher=}}</ref>.
